        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Make Energy Affordable Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the President to report on the rising energy prices. In addition, the President must provide updates on residential energy price trends, impacts of energy prices on low-income households, and actions by federal agencies to mitigate energy price increases.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
